headline: Jabil Reduces Greenhouse Gas Emissions by Nearly Half Compared to Baseline, Releases Fiscal Year 2024 Sustainability Progress Report
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., March 03, 2025--Jabil Inc. (NYSE: JBL) has released its fiscal year 2024 Sustainability Progress Report, detailing the strides the company has made toward achieving its five-year sustainability goals. The report highlights Jabil’s substantial progress in reducing operational greenhouse gas emissions, diverting waste from landfills, and giving back to the communities where employees live and work.
